t means (108) on the rotational speed of the input member (102) is reduced below the first predetermined speed (SI), wherein the input member (102) is rotatably connected to a crankshaft (IOC) of an engine (10); the output shaft (120) is coupled to an air compressor of a supercharger (10S); the first predetermined speed (SI) of the input member (102) corresponds to a lower operating speed of the engine (10); the second predetermined speed (S2) corresponds to a higher operating speed of the engine (10); 

